      "comment_id" : 80057255,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Note that this can also be configured on a reader using <code>without()</code> as in: <code>mapper.reader().without(DeserializationFeature.FAIL_ON_UNKNO&zwnj;&#8203;WN_PROPERTIES)</code>"
