    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>One other possibility is, if you want to ignore all unknown properties, you can configure the mapper as follows:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mapper.configure(DeserializationFeature.FAIL_ON_UNKNOWN_PROPERTIES, false);\n</code></pre>\n"
