      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "&quot;Why do we have mixins when we have withoutAttribute() ?&quot; -  Mixins cannot be set dynamically. <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/11849523/3105386\">stackoverflow.com/a/11849523/3105386</a>, while we can do that with &quot;withoutAttributes&quot;. That might be one of the reason."
